imdb.plot outline: When Miguel Angel Ruizpalacios is unjustly accused of fraud by his cousin, his family loses their entire fortune, leaving them on the streets. Their only option is to reside in a middle-class neighborhood called the Nopalera, in a home inhabited by the Menchaca family. These two very different families must learn to live with each other until Miguel Angel recovers his fortune and clears his name.
